      <div class="tips">
        <h3 class="mini-headers">Tips</h3>
        <ol>
          <li class="tip">You don’t have to know everything! - The misconception with Investment banking is that you’ve got to know everything, that isn’t exactly true. Be approachable,confident but most of all be hardworking.</li>
          <li class="tip">Your personality is everything - In IB you’re working 12-16 hour days, they want to know that you’re someone who can get on with the people around you.</li>
          <li class="tip">Know what they want - What are your motivations? when did you show teamwork? what financial markets are you following? how commercially aware are you? when did you have an ethical dilemma? Recruiter will want to know all this information from you.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
